OL,5,G1900 GPs: Behind Closed Doors
OL,6,     FAnn visits Dr Amir to find out if
OL,7,     Fhe can shed light on her
OL,8,     Funexplained vaginal bleeding.
OL,9,     FLaura's heart condition is
OL,10,     Fexacerbated by her situation -
OL,11,     Fshe's about to be made homeless.
OL,12,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,13,     FNurse Chloe answers the call when
OL,14,     Fa toddler is brought in with
OL,15,     Fsepsis. Norman, 84, is brought in
OL,16,     Fafter falling out of his mobility
OL,17,     Fscooter.
